# AI Bot Detection Browser Extension - Project Rules

## Project Overview

Our browser extension detects AI bots on websites and monitors user interactions to identify potential privacy risks.

## Core Functionality

- **Bot Detection**: Automatically identifies AI chatbots and bots on websites
- **Conversation Monitoring**: Reads and analyzes bot-user conversations in real-time
- **Privacy Risk Assessment**: Detects when bots request personal/sensitive information
- **User Warning System**: Alerts users via popup when privacy risks are detected

## Conversation Pattern Recognition

The extension monitors conversation flows like:

```
Bot: [AI bot response]
User: [User input]
Bot: [AI bot response]
```

## Privacy Risk Detection

The extension warns users when bots request:

- Phone numbers
- Personal information
- Addresses
- Financial details
- Social security numbers
- Other sensitive data

## Technical Implementation

- **Browser Extension**: Chrome/Firefox compatible
- **Content Scripts**: Monitor webpage content and bot interactions
- **Background Scripts**: Process data and manage extension state
- **Popup Interface**: User warnings and settings
- **API Integration**: Gemini AI for enhanced bot detection

